---

## Workflow order

Run the scripts in the following order:

```text
1. energy.py
2. landscape.py
3. FRAGSTATS processing
4. analysis_OLS.py
5. sdm_analysis.R
6. figure.py
```

---

## How to run

### Python analysis

```bash
python analysis/analysis_OLS.py
```

### R SDM analysis

```bash
Rscript analysis/sdm_analysis.R
```

### Figure generation

```bash
python analysis/figure.py
```
